written and spoken English, so that they
are being retained, they are not just

00:18:14.904 --> 00:18:17.094
going in one ear and out of the other.

00:18:18.414 --> 00:18:24.734
Ultimately, an AI can help you in a myriad
of ways, it can correct you and explain

00:18:24.934 --> 00:18:27.484
your mistakes, but it can’t learn for you.

00:18:28.074 --> 00:18:33.564
It can make the journey to fluency
shorter, more accessible, and reduce the

00:18:33.564 --> 00:18:36.414
cost, but there will always be a journey.

00:18:37.464 --> 00:18:41.514
You’ve probably heard me say this
before, but the more you can learn

00:18:41.524 --> 00:18:47.554
to enjoy this journey, and enjoy the
process of learning and creating the

00:18:47.554 --> 00:18:53.344
knowledge inside your own head, then the
more satisfying not just the journey,

00:18:53.734 --> 00:18:56.184
but also the final results will be.

00:18:57.214 --> 00:18:58.154
Think about it this way.

00:18:58.884 --> 00:19:05.144
An AI assistant like ChatGPT might be able
to write you a perfectly correct email or

00:19:05.424 --> 00:19:10.674
sales letter to a customer, and win the
admiration of your boss and colleagues,

00:19:10.904 --> 00:19:12.934
it might even help get you a promotion.

00:19:13.974 --> 00:19:18.324
But will you really have learned
anything from it, will there be any

00:19:18.564 --> 00:19:21.234
huge inner satisfaction that you feel?

00:19:22.334 --> 00:19:26.504
Perhaps, but it’ll probably
be temporary, and you won’t

00:19:26.514 --> 00:19:28.674
necessarily have internalised it.

00:19:29.644 --> 00:19:35.994
But if you treat this technology as
another way to improve your own linguistic

00:19:35.994 --> 00:19:41.344
knowledge, of improving your grammar and
vocabulary, and then the next time you

00:19:41.344 --> 00:19:48.234
can get there without AI, not only will
that be hugely satisfactory on an internal

00:19:48.234 --> 00:19:51.364
level, but it’ll be far more long-lasting.

00:19:52.404 --> 00:19:57.234
Ultimately, almost everyone learning
a language is doing so because they

00:19:57.234 --> 00:19:59.224
want to connect with other humans.

00:20:00.384 --> 00:20:07.134
Robots and AI can certainly help with
this, to some extent, but remember,

00:20:07.644 --> 00:20:12.464
to go all the way, you can’t rely
just on artificial intelligence.

